headline: Blue Sky Bank Turns to Jack Henry to Drive Innovation, Elevate Customer Service and Support Growth
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that Blue Sky Bank selected Jack Henry to provide customers with modern, competitive offerings through a blend of self-service and personal banking experiences. Jack Henry's commitment to research and development, along with its vision for the future, significantly influenced the bank's decision.
